    "(e.g., \"diabetes\" and \"cardiomyopathy\" are annotated for the mention, \"diabetes-induced cardiomyopathy\") • Annotate the mention representing the condition of disease (e.g., \"severe dyspnea\" rather than \"dyspnea\" and \"dry cough\" rather than \"cough\") • Do not annotate mentions, if the prefix of it is \"anti-\".",
    "• Do not annotate mentions concerning traditional medical diseases except \"Yang Deficiency\" and \"Yin Deficiency\".",
    "(e.g., liver-wind stirring syndrome, fluid-retention syndrome, and so on are not annotated)",
    "• Key-sentence is a condensed representation of the result or conclusion of the article.",
